  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">How you can help us recover unpaid child maintenance</h1>
      <div class="govuk-inset-text">
        As you use the Collect and Pay service, you do not need to tell us if you have not received a payment in full
      </div>
      <p class="govuk-body">Providing additional information might help us recover money owed to you.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">You can tell us anything relevant about the paying parent, for example:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-!-margin-bottom-7">
        <li>new contact details or addresses</li>
        <li>details of new employment</li>
        <li>information about their financial situation</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="govuk-body">We will not tell the paying parent that you've shared information with us.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">Weâ€™ll try to recover unpaid child maintenance whether you give us extra information or not.</p>
      
      

      <form action="" method="POST">
        {{ govukCharacterCount({
          name: "more-detail-on-file",
          id: "more-detail-on-file",
          maxlength: "600",
          rows: "8",
          label: {
            text: "Provide details of the information you are submitting",
            classes: "govuk-label--m"
          }
        }) }}

        <h2>Attachments</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">You can attach a file or photograph to support the information you provide.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">The maximum file size is 20MB and you can upload up to 7 files at a time.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">File names must only include letters a to z, numbers 0 to 9 and apostrophes. File type must be a PDF, JPEG, JPG, GIF, PNG, TIFF or TIF.</p>

